snippet.title: Lumberhill announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist on Steam! https://bit.ly/3ddKOKd

Sharpen your axe and join this hilariously chaotic co-op with Lumberjacks desperately trying to get their job done when literally everything gets in their way! Race against the clock, collect orders, fight wildfires, pirates and extremely annoying monkeys! Unlock tons of new skins and worlds playing in co-op, PVP or solo mode!

Developer: 2BIGO Studio
Publisher: Another Road Publishing (tinyurl.com/y83dj8wd)

Follow us!

Twitter: https://tinyurl.com/y9ulh5vf
